This paper deals with the problem of verifying the accuracy of information in Wikipedia articles, which is a natural language processing task. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.AI, cs.DL, cs.LG) techniques for building and evaluating algorithmic models.
